cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with natural language generation and computer vision, which are both covered by cs.CL and cs.CV. The use of human annotations and optimization for quick and accurate comprehension suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by cs.AI and cs.LG. Finally, the creation of a new dataset and the evaluation of the system suggest a focus on information retrieval, covered by cs.IR.
